    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好迎接一场前所未有的甜蜜冒险了吗？和 <strong>Sugar Rush</strong> 一起踏上美味之旅吧！这款终极糖果风格的点击游戏将满足你的甜食欲望，并考验你的战略技巧！🍬</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>语言支持：</strong> 我们支持多种语言，让来自世界各地的玩家都能尽情享受这场冒险！无论你喜欢英语、西班牙语、法语、德语、日语、韩语或其他语言，都能在自己的母语中畅玩！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301630/extras/image.png?t=1756241544\" /></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>活动：</strong> 准备迎接刺激的活动，让你的游戏体验更加精彩！限时挑战、特别奖励和节日庆典正等着你！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301630/extras/imagex.png?t=1756241544\" /></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>离线收入：</strong> 即使你没有主动点击，你的糖果帝国也会不断繁荣！回到游戏时收集利润和奖励，感谢你对糖果事业的坚持！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301630/extras/Skærmbillede_2024-11-27_213058.png?t=1756241544\" /></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>好友系统：</strong> 与其他糖果爱好者组队！与朋友连接，互相帮助，发送和接收礼物，共同进步！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301630/extras/Friend.png?t=1756241544\" /></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>自动化：</strong> 轻松休息而不减速！设置经理替你点击并生产糖果。坐下来放松，看着你的糖果王国轻松成长！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301630/extras/managers.png?t=1756241544\" /></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>每日奖励：</strong> 每天登录即可领取奖励！你玩得越多，奖励就越甜。不要错过每天等待你的美味惊喜！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301630/extras/Spin.png?t=1756241544\" /></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>更多内容：</strong> 探索充满惊喜、挑战和无限可能的世界。定期更新、新功能和活跃的社区，让乐趣永不停歇！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备释放这份甜蜜了吗？踏上糖果点击冒险，成为终极的 <strong>Sugar Rush 大师</strong>！立即下载，让甜蜜风暴开始吧！🍭</p>",
